{"id":35411,"date":"2024-01-23T00:58:00","date_gmt":"2022-06-22T19:28:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=35411"},"modified":"2024-10-19T20:53:17","modified_gmt":"2024-10-19T15:23:17","slug":"sleeper-chair","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sleeper-chair\/","title":{"rendered":"5 Comfortable Sleeper Chair Designs To Create A Cosy Nook At Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Is your living room feeling left out? Make it a warm and cosy space with these comfy sleeper chair designs!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A good home has all the fundamentals, a great one comprises the right design aesthetics. From choosing the right wall paint to learning about furnishings and even the slightest upholstery details, your home embraces the true essence of your personality. It reflects how you perceive yourself in the mirror. While some of you may be able to grasp the concept of interiors easily, a few others are always struggling to find that right piece that speaks out to them. Or what you have at home may not be as expressive as you\u2019d want it to be. In cases like these, fetching inspiration on the internet can be a great mood booster. And taking inspiration into consideration, here\u2019s a whittled-down list of some of our finest and comfiest sleeper chair designs. Have a look!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get A Sleeper Chair With Pull-Out Mattress<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your home demands space-saving furniture, a pull-out mattress lounge can be a great addition to your living room. This gorgeous mustard yellow sleeper chair sits beautifully in front of a French window with sheer curtains. The setup is perfect for an evening of watching movies or spending time with friends and folks. Your sleeper chair can daylight as an entertaining accent chair and then evolve into a chair sleeper sofa by night for guests to sleep on. Simply perfect!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012414\/get-a-sleeper-chair-with-pull-out-mattress.jpg\" alt=\"A convertible mustard-yellow sleeper chair into a pull-out mattress lounge\" class=\"wp-image-35412\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012414\/get-a-sleeper-chair-with-pull-out-mattress.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012414\/get-a-sleeper-chair-with-pull-out-mattress-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012414\/get-a-sleeper-chair-with-pull-out-mattress-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012414\/get-a-sleeper-chair-with-pull-out-mattress-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Convert your sleeper chair into a pull-out mattress<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modular Sleeper Chair With L-Shaped Headrest For Your Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Imagine a dreamy home with white walls and hardwood floors. In a corner, nestles your comfiest furniture \u2014 a modular sleeper chair with an L-shaped headrest, white bedding, pillows and a duvet. Now isn\u2019t that a dreamy bedroom setting! We love this beige sleeper chair that sits beautifully in this bedroom, making it a class apart.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012616\/modular-sleeper-chair-with-l-shaped-headrest-for-your-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"A modular sleeper chair with l-shaped headrest\" class=\"wp-image-35413\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012616\/modular-sleeper-chair-with-l-shaped-headrest-for-your-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012616\/modular-sleeper-chair-with-l-shaped-headrest-for-your-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012616\/modular-sleeper-chair-with-l-shaped-headrest-for-your-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012616\/modular-sleeper-chair-with-l-shaped-headrest-for-your-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">L-shaped headrest for a comfortable corner<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Lovely Pastel Diamond-Tufted Folding Sleeper Chair In A Bright Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Vibrant boho vibes are the loveliest in any home setting. They add so much character to your abode and act as a fun <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/home-decor-trends-2023\/\">decor trend<\/a> that we have seen many try out in recent years. If your living room is a fun entertaining zone, you can double up your level of comfort by replacing your regular accent chair with a diamond-tufted folding sleeper chair. Something like this pretty-in-pink sleeper chair that stands out against the teal sofa and wooden centre table. A sight worth falling in love with.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27012819\/a-lovely-pastel-diamond-tufted-folding-sleeper-chair-in-a-bright-room.jpg\" alt=\"A pastel diamond-tufted folding sleeper chair for bright room\" class=\"wp-image-35414\" srcset=\"https:\/